say, that's not quite what they mean.

00:06:46.650 --> 00:06:46.800
&gt;&gt; Right.

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:48.440
&gt;&gt; That's one thing I can do now.

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:52.120
I can go, if someone was quoting
The Evening Star, I can go now

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:55.020
and check The Evening Star
and use the primary source.

00:06:55.020 --> 00:06:58.120
So, yeah.

